radiographic_examinations.findings: The uterus measures 9.0 x 3.8 x 5.5 cm, normal in size and shape. Endometrium measures 2 mm, appears normal. A 1.3 x 1.3 x 1.1 cm round slightly hyperechoic structure in the endometrial cavity to the right of midline without demonstrated vascularity. No vascularized retained products of conception. Right ovary measures 3.2 x 2.4 x 3.3 cm and left ovary measures 2.6 x 1.9 x 2.7 cm with normal arterial and venous flow. A small amount of pelvic free fluid is noted.
